name: HoleyMoley
description: Holey Moley was made in a 1 week time span for the Brackeys game jam#3 the theme was holes. This is my first game jam and my first actual release of a full game, im not the best artist but i still hope you can enjoy the game. The music was made using bosca ceoil and sxfr. Hint(sometimes there are multiple moles in a single hole so always double click);) Features not bugs.
